# Architectural Decisions

Document design choices, technology selections, and strategic directions.

## When to Write

- After making significant architectural decisions
- When selecting technologies or approaches
- When establishing project-wide conventions
- When defining component boundaries

## File Naming

`YYYY-MM-DD-descriptive-name.memory.md`

Example: `2025-12-19-hindsight-memory-architecture.memory.md`

## Template

See `../../templates/memory.template.md` for the standard format.
